      "updated": 1700000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Container: litellm\nImage: ghcr.io/berriai/litellm-database:main-latest\nPort: 4000 / HTTP\n\nRessources:\n  CPU:    250m (req) → 1000m (limit)\n  Memory: 512Mi (req) → 2Gi (limit)\n\nHealth:\n  Liveness:  GET /health/liveliness\n  Readiness: GET /health/readiness\n\nEnv (depuis Secret litellm-secrets):\n  LITELLM_MASTER_KEY, LITELLM_SALT_KEY\n  DATABASE_URL → postgresql://litellm-postgres:5432/litellm\n  STORE_MODEL_IN_DB=true | LITELLM_MODE=PRODUCTION\n\nVolumes:\n  /app/config.yaml  ← ConfigMap: litellm-config\n  /data             ← PVC: litellm-data-pvc (5Gi)",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Container: litellm\nImage: ghcr.io/berriai/litellm-database:main-latest\nPort: 4000 / HTTP\n\nRessources:\n  CPU:    250m (req) → 1000m (limit)\n  Memory: 512Mi (req) → 2Gi (limit)\n\nHealth:\n  Liveness:  GET /health/liveliness\n  Readiness: GET /health/readiness\n\nEnv (depuis Secret litellm-secrets):\n  LITELLM_MASTER_KEY, LITELLM_SALT_KEY\n  DATABASE_URL → postgresql://litellm-postgres:5432/litellm\n  STORE_MODEL_IN_DB=true | LITELLM_MODE=PRODUCTION\n\nVolumes:\n  /app/config.yaml  ← ConfigMap: litellm-config\n  /data             ← PVC: litellm-data-pvc (5Gi)",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.4
