      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Container: postgres\nImage: postgres:15-alpine\nPort: 5432 / TCP\n\nBase de données:\n  DB:   litellm\n  User: litellm\n  PGDATA: /var/lib/postgresql/data/pgdata\n\nRessources:\n  CPU:    100m (req) → 500m (limit)\n  Memory: 256Mi (req) → 1Gi (limit)\n\nHealth:\n  Liveness + Readiness: pg_isready\n\nPersistance:\n  PVC: postgres-data (10Gi)\n  StorageClass: standard-rwo\n\nService (Headless): litellm-postgres:5432",
