      "originalText": "APIs LLM Externes\n\nOpenAI API\nAnthropic API\nGoogle Vertex AI\nAzure OpenAI\nAWS Bedrock\nMistral AI\n... (tout provider)\n\nEndpoints LiteLLM:\n  GET  /v1/models\n  POST /v1/chat/completions\n  POST /v1/embeddings\n  GET  /ui  (Admin Panel)\n  GET  /docs  (Swagger)\n  GET  /health/readiness",
